        <item>
            <title>「頭 7」巴士現身街頭，市民笑言靈車降臨，其實只是螢幕故障</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/16/kmb-3/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=kmb-3</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/16/kmb-3/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 16 Apr 2025 12:01:08 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1303758</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近日一輛行駛於大埔至九龍城碼頭的 75X 九巴雙層巴士成為網民焦點，原因並非車型新穎或改道行駛，而是電子顯示屏故障，只顯示出「頭 7」兩字，乍看之下有如「靈車」出巡，令人啼笑皆非。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416747422.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1303765" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416747422-694x385.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416747422-694x385.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416747422.jpg 876w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>事源有網民於 Facebook 羣組「是日快快 &#8211; 巴士即日相」上載一張照片，顯示該輛九巴巴士正駛經大埔，車頭電子顯示屏只剩「頭 7」兩字。無論從左至右還是右至左閲讀，字面意義都令人聯想到忌諱話題，有網民戲言「回魂夜專用」，更有人指「真係大吉利是」，引來大批留言瘋傳。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_47_42.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1303767" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_47_42-404x580.jpg" alt="" width="604" height="867" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_47_42-404x580.jpg 404w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_47_42.jpg 627w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 604px" /></a></p><p>雖然巴士前擋風玻璃上已貼有清晰的「75X」紙牌標示實際路線，但仍無阻市民將畫面截圖瘋傳。評論區中，不少人紛紛發表搞笑回應：「即刻落車好 D」、「好心停左個牌，人地鬼知你壞 D 乜」、「好心就索性熄左佢或者轉左佢」，更有人開玩笑問：「如果夜晚見到依架車，你搭嗎？👻」亦有市民聯想到香港的殯儀文化，笑問「去和合石專車？」、甚至諷刺地説「搭呢架車真係要回家跨火盤先可以洗衰氣」，氣氛詼諧幽默。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_49_042-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303766" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_49_042-1-694x237.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="237" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_49_042-1-694x237.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_49_042-1.jpg 1020w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_49_042.jpg"><br /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_49_102.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303760" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_49_102.jpg" alt="" width="494" height="172" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_49_152.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303761" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_49_152-694x170.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="170" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_49_152-694x170.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_49_152.jpg 1248w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_47_592.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303762" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_47_592-694x192.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="192" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_47_592-694x192.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_47_592.jpg 700w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_48_232.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303763" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_48_232.jpg" alt="" width="484" height="166" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_48_442.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303764" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250416_7_48_442.jpg" alt="" width="692" height="176" /></a></p><p>根據九巴官網資訊，該輛巴士正常行駛 75X 路線，由大埔（富善）開往九龍城碼頭，而今次意外純屬電子顯示故障，與實際營運無關。事件未有影響班次或乘客安全。</p><p>此事雖然只是小小技術失誤，但因其字面效果太過「撞鬼」，意外為網民帶來一陣笑彈。也提醒相關部門，螢幕錯誤有時不止於資訊錯漏，還可能一不小心，變成另類都市傳説。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/1643712612558918/search/?q=75X">Facebook</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/16/kmb-3/fun-tech/">「頭 7」巴士現身街頭，市民笑言靈車降臨，其實只是螢幕故障</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/16/kmb-3/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
